<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.200573>
    dc:description "FIGURES 46 – 51. Grass living Thripinae. (46) Karphothrips dugdalei, tergites VII – IX. Kranzithrips mareebai 47 – 51: (47) tergites VII – IX; (48) meso & metanota; (49) sternites V – VI; (50) male tergites VII – IX; (51) head & pronotum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/200573/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.200571>
    dc:description "FIGURES 31 – 37. Bregmatothrips australis. (31) head & pronotum; (32) ventral view of head & prothorax; (33) tergites VII – X; (34) male tergites VII – IX; (35) meso & metanota with wing lobe; (36 – 37) sternites VI – VII." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/200571/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

